Var 
Area,Perimeter,Radious:real

Inicio
escreva ("Input the Radious: ")
leia (Radious)
Area<-(pi*Radious^2)
Perimeter<-(2*pi*Radious)
escreva ("The Area is: ",Area,"The Perimeter is: ",Perimeter)
Fimalgoritmo
